{
  "uid": "hz-cp-health",
  "title": "HZ CP \u2014 Subsystem Health",
  "schemaVersion": 38,
  "version": 1,
  "refresh": "10s",
  "time": {
    "from": "now-1h",
    "to": "now"
  },
  "timepicker": {},
  "tags": [
    "hazelcast",
    "cp-subsystem",
    "health"
  ],
  "templating": {
    "list": [
      {
        "name": "cluster",
        "label": "Cluster",
        "type": "query",
        "datasource": {
          "type": "prometheus",
          "uid": "prometheus"
        },
        "definition": "label_values(hz_runtime_uptime, mc_cluster)",
        "query": {
          "query": "label_values(hz_runtime_uptime, mc_cluster)",
          "refId": "SV"
        },
        "sort": 1,
        "multi": false,
        "includeAll": false,
        "refresh": 2,
        "hide": 0,
        "current": {}
      },
      {
        "name": "cp_group",
        "label": "CP Group",
        "type": "query",
        "datasource": {
          "type": "prometheus",
          "uid": "prometheus"
        },
        "definition": "label_values(hz_raft_group_term{mc_cluster=\"$cluster\"}, name)",
        "query": {
          "query": "label_values(hz_raft_group_term{mc_cluster=\"$cluster\"}, name)",
          "refId": "SV"
        },
        "sort": 1,
        "multi": true,
        "includeAll": true,
        "allValue": ".*",
        "refresh": 2,
        "hide": 0,
        "current": {}
      },
      {
        "name": "member",
        "label": "Member",
        "type": "query",
        "datasource": {
          "type": "prometheus",
          "uid": "prometheus"
        },
        "definition": "label_values(hz_runtime_uptime{mc_cluster=\"$cluster\"}, mc_member)",
        "query": {
          "query": "label_values(hz_runtime_uptime{mc_cluster=\"$cluster\"}, mc_member)",
          "refId": "SV"
        },
        "sort": 1,
        "multi": true,
        "includeAll": true,
        "allValue": ".*",
        "refresh": 2,
        "hide": 0,
        "current": {}
      }
    ]
  },
  "panels": [
    {
      "id": 1,
      "type": "text",
      "title": "",
      "gridPos": {
        "x": 0,
        "y": 0,
        "w": 24,
        "h": 8
      },
      "options": {
        "mode": "markdown",
        "content": "## CP Subsystem Health\n\nOperational health view of the **CP Subsystem as a whole** \u2014 cluster membership, group status, quorum integrity, and election activity.\nUse this as the first dashboard to open when investigating CP-related incidents.\n\n**Key questions this dashboard answers:**\n- Are all 5 CP members active and reachable? *(Active / Missing Members)*\n- Is every CP group running with a full quorum of 3 members? *(Group Member Count)*\n- Which member leads which group right now, and has that changed recently? *(Leader Timeline)*\n- Is there unusual election activity across any group? *(Election stat + Group Status table)*\n\n**Filters:** **Cluster** selects the environment. **CP Group** narrows the Raft-level panels to specific groups.\n\n**Normal state:** 5 active members, 0 missing, every group has 3 members, stable leaders, 0 elections in the last 15 min.\n**Incident checklist:** missing members \u2192 check Docker health; group member count drops \u2192 check Raft log for partitions; repeated elections \u2192 check GC pauses and network latency."
      },
      "transparent": true
    },
    {
      "id": 2,
      "type": "row",
      "title": "Cluster Membership",
      "collapsed": false,
      "gridPos": {
        "x": 0,
        "y": 8,
        "w": 24,
        "h": 1
      },
      "panels": []
    },
    {
      "id": 3,
      "type": "stat",
      "title": "Reachable CP Members",
      "description": "CP members currently reachable: activeMembers \u2212 missingMembers. Reacts immediately when a member drops. activeMembers alone stays at 5 until formal removal (missing-cp-member-auto-removal-seconds = 8 h).",
      "datasource": {
        "type": "prometheus",
        "uid": "prometheus"
      },
      "gridPos": {
        "x": 0,
        "y": 9,
        "w": 6,
        "h": 5
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "datasource": {
            "type": "prometheus",
            "uid": "prometheus"
          },
          "expr": "max(hz_raft_metadata_activeMembers{mc_cluster=\"$cluster\"}) - max(hz_raft_missingMembers{mc_cluster=\"$cluster\"})",
          "legendFormat": "reachable members",
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ],
      "options": {
        "reduceOptions": {
          "calcs": [
            "lastNotNull"
          ]
        },
        "colorMode": "background",
        "graphMode": "area",
        "textMode": "auto",
        "orientation": "auto"
      },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "decimals": 0,
          "unit": "short",
          "thresholds": {
            "mode": "absolute",
            "steps": [
              {
                "color": "red",
                "value": 0
              },
              {
                "color": "yellow",
                "value": 3
              },
              {
                "color": "green",
                "value": 5
              }
            ]
          }
        },
        "overrides": []
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 4,
      "type": "stat",
      "title": "Missing CP Members",
      "description": "Members unreachable but not yet auto-removed. Any value > 0 requires immediate attention.",
      "datasource": {
        "type": "prometheus",
        "uid": "prometheus"
      },
      "gridPos": {
        "x": 6,
        "y": 9,
        "w": 6,
        "h": 5
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "datasource": {
            "type": "prometheus",
            "uid": "prometheus"
          },
          "expr": "max(hz_raft_missingMembers{mc_cluster=\"$cluster\"})",
          "legendFormat": "missing",
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ],
      "options": {
        "reduceOptions": {
          "calcs": [
            "lastNotNull"
          ]
        },
        "colorMode": "background",
        "graphMode": "area",
        "textMode": "auto",
        "orientation": "auto"
      },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "decimals": 0,
          "unit": "short",
          "thresholds": {
            "mode": "absolute",
            "steps": [
              {
                "color": "green",
                "value": 0
              },
              {
                "color": "red",
                "value": 1
              }
            ]
          }
        },
        "overrides": []
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 5,
      "type": "stat",
      "title": "CP Groups",
      "description": "Total CP groups tracked by METADATA. Increases as new groups are created on first use.",
      "datasource": {
        "type": "prometheus",
        "uid": "prometheus"
      },
      "gridPos": {
        "x": 12,
        "y": 9,
        "w": 6,
        "h": 5
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "datasource": {
            "type": "prometheus",
            "uid": "prometheus"
          },
          "expr": "max(hz_raft_metadata_groups{mc_cluster=\"$cluster\"})",
          "legendFormat": "groups",
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ],
      "options": {
        "reduceOptions": {
          "calcs": [
            "lastNotNull"
          ]
        },
        "colorMode": "value",
        "graphMode": "area",
        "textMode": "auto",
        "orientation": "auto"
      },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "decimals": 0,
          "unit": "short",
          "thresholds": {
            "mode": "absolute",
            "steps": [
              {
                "color": "blue",
                "value": 0
              }
            ]
          }
        },
        "overrides": []
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 6,
      "type": "stat",
      "title": "Terminated Groups",
      "description": "Terminated Raft node group IDs. Should be 0 in normal operation.",
      "datasource": {
        "type": "prometheus",
        "uid": "prometheus"
      },
      "gridPos": {
        "x": 18,
        "y": 9,
        "w": 6,
        "h": 5
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "datasource": {
            "type": "prometheus",
            "uid": "prometheus"
          },
          "expr": "max(hz_raft_terminatedRaftNodeGroupIds{mc_cluster=\"$cluster\"})",
          "legendFormat": "terminated",
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ],
      "options": {
        "reduceOptions": {
          "calcs": [
            "lastNotNull"
          ]
        },
        "colorMode": "background",
        "graphMode": "area",
        "textMode": "auto",
        "orientation": "auto"
      },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "decimals": 0,
          "unit": "short",
          "thresholds": {
            "mode": "absolute",
            "steps": [
              {
                "color": "green",
                "value": 0
              },
              {
                "color": "orange",
                "value": 1
              }
            ]
          }
        },
        "overrides": []
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 7,
      "type": "stat",
      "title": "Leader Elections (last 15 min)",
      "description": "Total elections across all CP groups in the last 15 minutes. Occasional value of 1 is normal after a restart; persistent non-zero is a warning.",
      "datasource": {
        "type": "prometheus",
        "uid": "prometheus"
      },
      "gridPos": {
        "x": 0,
        "y": 14,
        "w": 6,
        "h": 4
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "datasource": {
            "type": "prometheus",
            "uid": "prometheus"
          },
          "expr": "sum(changes(hz_raft_group_term{mc_cluster=\"$cluster\"}[15m]))",
          "legendFormat": "elections",
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ],
      "options": {
        "reduceOptions": {
          "calcs": [
            "lastNotNull"
          ]
        },
        "colorMode": "background",
        "graphMode": "area",
        "textMode": "auto",
        "orientation": "auto"
      },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "decimals": 0,
          "unit": "short",
          "thresholds": {
            "mode": "absolute",
            "steps": [
              {
                "color": "green",
                "value": 0
              },
              {
                "color": "yellow",
                "value": 1
              },
              {
                "color": "red",
                "value": 5
              }
            ]
          }
        },
        "overrides": []
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 8,
      "type": "stat",
      "title": "Max Commit Lag",
      "description": "Largest replication lag across all groups and members right now (entries committed but not applied). Should be near 0.",
      "datasource": {
        "type": "prometheus",
        "uid": "prometheus"
      },
      "gridPos": {
        "x": 6,
        "y": 14,
        "w": 6,
        "h": 4
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "datasource": {
            "type": "prometheus",
            "uid": "prometheus"
          },
          "expr": "max(hz_raft_group_commitIndex{mc_cluster=\"$cluster\"} - hz_raft_group_lastApplied{mc_cluster=\"$cluster\"})",
          "legendFormat": "entries",
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ],
      "options": {
        "reduceOptions": {
          "calcs": [
            "lastNotNull"
          ]
        },
        "colorMode": "background",
        "graphMode": "area",
        "textMode": "auto",
        "orientation": "auto"
      },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "decimals": 0,
          "unit": "short",
          "thresholds": {
            "mode": "absolute",
            "steps": [
              {
                "color": "green",
                "value": 0
              },
              {
                "color": "yellow",
                "value": 50
              },
              {
                "color": "red",
                "value": 200
              }
            ]
          }
        },
        "overrides": []
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 9,
      "type": "stat",
      "title": "Raft Nodes per Member",
      "description": "Number of Raft node instances on each cluster member. Should equal the number of CP groups that member participates in.",
      "datasource": {
        "type": "prometheus",
        "uid": "prometheus"
      },
      "gridPos": {
        "x": 12,
        "y": 14,
        "w": 12,
        "h": 4
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "datasource": {
            "type": "prometheus",
            "uid": "prometheus"
          },
          "expr": "max by (mc_member) (hz_raft_nodes{mc_cluster=\"$cluster\"})",
          "legendFormat": "{{mc_member}}",
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ],
      "options": {
        "reduceOptions": {
          "calcs": [
            "lastNotNull"
          ]
        },
        "colorMode": "value",
        "graphMode": "area",
        "textMode": "auto",
        "orientation": "auto"
      },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "decimals": 0,
          "unit": "short",
          "thresholds": {
            "mode": "absolute",
            "steps": [
              {
                "color": "blue",
                "value": 0
              }
            ]
          }
        },
        "overrides": []
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 10,
      "type": "row",
      "title": "Quorum & Leadership",
      "collapsed": false,
      "gridPos": {
        "x": 0,
        "y": 18,
        "w": 24,
        "h": 1
      },
      "panels": []
    },
    {
      "id": 11,
      "type": "stat",
      "title": "Group Member Count",
      "description": "Members in each Raft group. group-size=3. At 2 the group is degraded but functional. At 1 the group is unavailable \u2014 no reads or writes can complete.",
      "datasource": {
        "type": "prometheus",
        "uid": "prometheus"
      },
      "gridPos": {
        "x": 0,
        "y": 19,
        "w": 8,
        "h": 8
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "datasource": {
            "type": "prometheus",
            "uid": "prometheus"
          },
          "expr": "min by (name) (hz_raft_group_memberCount{mc_cluster=\"$cluster\", name=~\"$cp_group\"})",
          "legendFormat": "{{name}}",
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ],
      "options": {
        "reduceOptions": {
          "calcs": [
            "lastNotNull"
          ]
        },
        "colorMode": "background",
        "graphMode": "area",
        "textMode": "auto",
        "orientation": "auto"
      },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "decimals": 0,
          "unit": "short",
          "thresholds": {
            "mode": "absolute",
            "steps": [
              {
                "color": "red",
                "value": 0
              },
              {
                "color": "orange",
                "value": 2
              },
              {
                "color": "green",
                "value": 3
              }
            ]
          }
        },
        "overrides": []
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 12,
      "type": "state-timeline",
      "title": "Leader per CP Group (timeline)",
      "description": "One horizontal track per (group, member) pair. A filled band means that member is currently leader of that group. Band transitions mark elections.",
      "datasource": {
        "type": "prometheus",
        "uid": "prometheus"
      },
      "gridPos": {
        "x": 8,
        "y": 19,
        "w": 16,
        "h": 8
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "datasource": {
            "type": "prometheus",
            "uid": "prometheus"
          },
          "expr": "hz_raft_group_term{mc_cluster=\"$cluster\", role=\"LEADER\", name=~\"$cp_group\"}",
          "legendFormat": "{{name}} \u2192 {{mc_member}}",
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ],
      "options": {
        "mergeValues": true,
        "showValue": "never",
        "alignValue": "center",
        "rowHeight": 0.9,
        "tooltip": {
          "mode": "single"
        },
        "legend": {
          "displayMode": "list",
          "placement": "bottom"
        }
      },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "custom": {
            "lineWidth": 0,
            "fillOpacity": 70
          }
        },
        "overrides": []
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 13,
      "type": "row",
      "title": "Group Status Detail",
      "collapsed": false,
      "gridPos": {
        "x": 0,
        "y": 27,
        "w": 24,
        "h": 1
      },
      "panels": []
    },
    {
      "id": 14,
      "type": "table",
      "title": "CP Group Status",
      "description": "Snapshot of key Raft state for every group \u00d7 member combination. Use the CP Group filter to narrow. 'role' shows LEADER or FOLLOWER.",
      "datasource": {
        "type": "prometheus",
        "uid": "prometheus"
      },
      "gridPos": {
        "x": 0,
        "y": 28,
        "w": 24,
        "h": 10
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "datasource": {
            "type": "prometheus",
            "uid": "prometheus"
          },
          "expr": "hz_raft_group_term{mc_cluster=\"$cluster\", name=~\"$cp_group\"}",
          "legendFormat": "term",
          "instant": true,
          "refId": "A"
        },
        {
          "datasource": {
            "type": "prometheus",
            "uid": "prometheus"
          },
          "expr": "hz_raft_group_commitIndex{mc_cluster=\"$cluster\", name=~\"$cp_group\"}",
          "legendFormat": "commitIndex",
          "instant": true,
          "refId": "B"
        },
        {
          "datasource": {
            "type": "prometheus",
            "uid": "prometheus"
          },
          "expr": "hz_raft_group_lastApplied{mc_cluster=\"$cluster\", name=~\"$cp_group\"}",
          "legendFormat": "lastApplied",
          "instant": true,
          "refId": "C"
        },
        {
          "datasource": {
            "type": "prometheus",
            "uid": "prometheus"
          },
          "expr": "hz_raft_group_memberCount{mc_cluster=\"$cluster\", name=~\"$cp_group\"}",
          "legendFormat": "memberCount",
          "instant": true,
          "refId": "D"
        },
        {
          "datasource": {
            "type": "prometheus",
            "uid": "prometheus"
          },
          "expr": "hz_raft_group_availableLogCapacity{mc_cluster=\"$cluster\", name=~\"$cp_group\"}",
          "legendFormat": "logCapacity",
          "instant": true,
          "refId": "E"
        }
      ],
      "options": {
        "sortBy": [
          {
            "displayName": "name"
          },
          {
            "displayName": "mc_member"
          }
        ]
      },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "decimals": 0
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "transformations": [
        {
          "id": "merge",
          "options": {}
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 15,
      "type": "row",
      "title": "Scrape & MC Health",
      "collapsed": false,
      "gridPos": {
        "x": 0,
        "y": 38,
        "w": 24,
        "h": 1
      },
      "panels": []
    },
    {
      "id": 16,
      "type": "timeseries",
      "title": "Management Center Scrape",
      "description": "1 = Prometheus is successfully scraping Management Center. 0 = all CP metrics are stale.",
      "datasource": {
        "type": "prometheus",
        "uid": "prometheus"
      },
      "gridPos": {
        "x": 0,
        "y": 39,
        "w": 8,
        "h": 6
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "datasource": {
            "type": "prometheus",
            "uid": "prometheus"
          },
          "expr": "up{job=\"hazelcast\"}",
          "legendFormat": "MC scrape",
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ],
      "options": {
        "tooltip": {
          "mode": "multi"
        },
        "legend": {
          "displayMode": "table",
          "placement": "bottom",
          "calcs": [
            "lastNotNull",
            "max"
          ]
        }
      },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "custom": {
            "lineWidth": 2,
            "fillOpacity": 6
          },
          "min": 0,
          "unit": "short"
        },
        "overrides": []
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 17,
      "type": "timeseries",
      "title": "MC Health Check Results",
      "description": "Health check status counts reported by each member to Management Center.",
      "datasource": {
        "type": "prometheus",
        "uid": "prometheus"
      },
      "gridPos": {
        "x": 8,
        "y": 39,
        "w": 16,
        "h": 6
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "datasource": {
            "type": "prometheus",
            "uid": "prometheus"
          },
          "expr": "hz_healthcheck_status_fail{mc_cluster=\"$cluster\"}",
          "legendFormat": "FAIL",
          "refId": "A"
        },
        {
          "datasource": {
            "type": "prometheus",
            "uid": "prometheus"
          },
          "expr": "hz_healthcheck_status_warning{mc_cluster=\"$cluster\"}",
          "legendFormat": "WARNING",
          "refId": "B"
        },
        {
          "datasource": {
            "type": "prometheus",
            "uid": "prometheus"
          },
          "expr": "hz_healthcheck_status_pass{mc_cluster=\"$cluster\"}",
          "legendFormat": "PASS",
          "refId": "C"
        }
      ],
      "options": {
        "tooltip": {
          "mode": "multi"
        },
        "legend": {
          "displayMode": "table",
          "placement": "bottom",
          "calcs": [
            "lastNotNull",
            "max"
          ]
        }
      },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "custom": {
            "lineWidth": 2,
            "fillOpacity": 6
          },
          "min": 0,
          "unit": "short"
        },
        "overrides": []
      }
    }
  ]
}